com.google.android.agera

Interface UpdateDispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Observable, Updatable

    public interface UpdateDispatcher
extends Observable, Updatable
    Passes on updates from an Updatable.update() call to any Updatable added using Observable.addUpdatable(com.google.android.agera.Updatable). It should be possible to call Updatable.update() from any thread.

    This interface should typically not be implemented by client code; the standard implementations obtainable from Observables.updateDispatcher() help implement Observables adhering to the contract.

      • Methods inherited from interface com.google.android.agera.Observable

        addUpdatable, removeUpdatable

      • Methods inherited from interface com.google.android.agera.Updatable

        update
